<h1>How to subscribe</h1>
<p>Subscribing to a podcast in a podcast app will automatically download new episodes.</p>

<h2 id="tab1" class="tab accordion" aria-controls="panel1" role="tab" tabindex="0">
    <svg class="icon icon-os icon-android"><use xlink:href="#icon-android"></use></svg> Android
</h2>
<div id="panel1" class="panel accordion" aria-labeledby="tab1" role="tabpanel">
    <ol>
        <li>Download <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.google.android.apps.podcasts&hl=en_US">Google Podcasts</a> or the podcast app of your choice.

        <li>Tap the <kbd><samp>Add new Podcast</samp></kbd> button.
        <br>
        <img src="{{metadata.cdn_url}}/img/subscribe-android-podcast-addict-01.png">

        <li>Tap the <kbd><samp>Search Engine</samp></kbd> tile.
        <br>
        <img src="{{metadata.cdn_url}}/img/subscribe-android-podcast-addict-02.png">

        <li>Search for <b>Ten to One</b>.
        <br>
        <img src="{{metadata.cdn_url}}/img/subscribe-android-podcast-addict-03.png">

        <li>Tap the <kbd><samp>Subscribe</samp></kbd> button.
        <br>
        <img src="{{metadata.cdn_url}}/img/subscribe-android-podcast-addict-04.png">

        <li>Tap the menu icon. Then tap <kbd><samp>Update</samp></kbd>, <kbd><samp>Automatic refresh</samp></kbd>, <kbd><samp>Enable Podcasts automatic refresh</samp></kbd>.
        <br>
        <img src="{{metadata.cdn_url}}/img/subscribe-android-podcast-addict-05.png">
        <img src="{{metadata.cdn_url}}/img/subscribe-android-podcast-addict-06.png">

        <li>Tap the <b>back button</b> to go back to Settings. Then tap <kbd><samp>Download</samp></kbd>, <kbd><samp>Automatic download</samp></kbd>. Now, whenever we release a new episode, it will automatically download to your phone.
        <br>
        <img src="{{metadata.cdn_url}}/img/subscribe-android-podcast-addict-07.png">

        <li>You will get a notification when an episode has downloaded. Tap the notification to see the new episode. Or, open the app and tap on the Ten to One tile.
        <br>
        <img src="{{metadata.cdn_url}}/img/subscribe-android-podcast-addict-08.png">
        <img src="{{metadata.cdn_url}}/img/subscribe-android-podcast-addict-09.png">

        <li>Tap the <b>Play</b> button to play the episode. If the episode has not downloaded, a Download button will be in place of the Play button. Tap <b>Download</b> to download the episode.
        <br>
        <img src="{{metadata.cdn_url}}/img/subscribe-android-podcast-addict-10.png">

        <li>Enjoy the podcast!
    </ol>
</div>

<h2 id="tab2" class="tab accordion" aria-controls="panel2" role="tab" tabindex="-1">
    <svg class="icon icon-os icon-appleinc"><use xlink:href="#icon-appleinc"></use></svg> iPhone or iPad
</h2>
<div id="panel2" class="panel accordion" aria-labeledby="tab2" role="tabpanel">
    <ol>
        <li>Open the <b>Podcasts</b> app on your iPhone or iPad.
        <br>
        <img src="{{metadata.cdn_url}}/img/subscribe-apple-1.png">

        <li>Tap the <kbd><samp>Search</samp></kbd> button in the bottom menu.
        <br>
        <img src="{{metadata.cdn_url}}/img/subscribe-apple-2.png">

        <li>Search for <b>Ten to One</b>.
        <br>
        <img src="{{metadata.cdn_url}}/img/subscribe-apple-3.png">

        <li>Find and tap on the Ten to One podcast (you might have to scroll down).
        <br>
        <img src="{{metadata.cdn_url}}/img/subscribe-apple-4.png">

        <li>Tap the <kbd><samp>Subscribe</samp></kbd> button.
        <br>
        <img src="{{metadata.cdn_url}}/img/subscribe-apple-5.png">

        <li>Tap the <kbd><samp>My Podcasts</samp></kbd> button. Then tap on any episode to download and listen.
        <br>
        <img src="{{metadata.cdn_url}}/img/subscribe-apple-6.png">

        <li>A new episode will be downloaded every two weeks.

        <li>Enjoy the podcast!
    </ol>
</div>

<h2 id="tab3" class="tab accordion" aria-controls="panel3" role="tab" tabindex="-1">
    <svg class="icon icon-os icon-windows8"><use xlink:href="#icon-windows8"></use></svg> Windows
</h2>
<div id="panel3" class="panel accordion" aria-labeledby="tab3" role="tabpanel">
    <ol>
        <li>Download and install <a href="https://www.apple.com/itunes/download/">iTunes</a>.
    	
        <li>Open iTunes and click <kbd><samp>File</samp></kbd>, then <kbd><samp>Subscribe to Podcast</samp></kbd>.
        <br>
        <img src="{{metadata.cdn_url}}/img/subscribe-windows-itunes-1.png">

        <li>Enter our URL: <b>http://tto.koser.us/feed.rss</b> and click <kbd><samp>OK</samp></kbd>.
        <br>
        <img src="{{metadata.cdn_url}}/img/subscribe-windows-itunes-2.png">

        <li>You do not need to sync, but you should select <kbd><samp>Automatically download new episodes for your subscriptions</samp></kbd>, then click <kbd><samp>Continue</samp></kbd>.
        <br>
        <img src="{{metadata.cdn_url}}/img/subscribe-windows-itunes-3.png">

        <li>Listen to an episode by double-clicking it.
        <br>
        <img src="{{metadata.cdn_url}}/img/subscribe-windows-itunes-4.png">    
        
        <li>To listen to our new episodes, just open iTunes. Any new episodes will be automatically downloaded.

        <li>Enjoy the podcast!
    </ol>
</div>